                      _numberFormat,
                      style: TextStyle(
                        color: Colors.white,
                        fontSize: 12,
                        fontWeight: FontWeight.bold,
                      ),
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
              ],
            ),
          ),

          // Display principal mejorado (como calculadora real)
          Expanded(
            flex: 2,
            child: Container(
              width: double.infinity,
              padding: EdgeInsets.all(12),
              decoration: BoxDecoration(
